    Implements Category, that represents a class of users within EQN network.

    Represents a clone user of an "original" user passing through a Split node.

    Represents a CloneUser with tracking capabilities.
    CountingUser
    Represents a user that incorporates counting capabilities, ie the user is provided with an internal counter.
    DadUser
    Defines the Dad User, ie any type of jEQN user that passing through a Fork Node is transformed in a Dad User - and associated to a set of Son Users
    Link

    TrackingPathUser
    Defines a user with path tracking capabilities.
